Nightreign Forsaken Hollows All Classes Ranked - Best & Worst You NEED To Know! Classes Tier List
In this Elden Ring Nightreign video, we're going to be bringing you a tier list for the 10 Nightfarers currently in the game. It's going to be a bit different than the tier list we did before. The first tier list we did was mostly focused on how beginner-friendly each class was, as well as how effective it was. But as time has passed and new meters have become a thing, as you know, patches to the game have happened. There's quite a lot to unpack in terms of how good each class actually is at the moment.
